CONCLUSION:

  1. Bank should focus on age group 28-35 with CIBIL_Score 0.3-0.5
  2. Bank has given most loans to the applicants who resides on tier-2 Region/City
  3. Bank has given most loans to Laborers whereas with higher credit loans were given to Managers.
  4. Bank should avoid giving loans to applicants who are married and have only higher education, the have loan repayment difficulties. Whereas Applicants who are married and have Academic degrees have repay the loan.
  5. Most loans applied for Repairs purpose are rejected
  6. Loans are mostly taken by Cash , it’s noticed Revolving Loans have more repayment difficulties.
